@startuml
actor Korisnik
participant "WinForms GUI" as GUI
participant "Forma" as Form
participant "Python/Exe" as Proc
participant "Temp datoteke" as Temp

Korisnik -> GUI: Učitaj sliku i odaberi modul
GUI -> Form: Proslijedi ulaz i parametre
Form -> Proc: Pokreni skriptu ili exe
Proc -> Temp: Snimi izlaz
Proc --> Form: Povratni status
Form -> GUI: Učitaj izlaz i prikaži
GUI --> Korisnik: Pregled i spremanje
@enduml
